bulletPoints: Architected and developed scalable microservices and web applications using TypeScript, JavaScript, and Python, ensuring high availability and performance across cloud platforms.
Led a cross-functional team of 3 developers in an Agile/Scrum environment, mentoring junior engineers and overseeing the full software development life cycle (SDLC).
Optimized complex PostgreSQL and MongoDB queries and schema designs, improving application response times by 30% and enhancing overall data integrity.
Partnered with product managers and stakeholders to translate business requirements into technical specifications, utilizing advanced debugging and problem-solving skills to maintain 99.9% uptime.
Engineered robust RESTful APIs and GraphQL endpoints using Node.js and Express, facilitating seamless data exchange between client-side and server-side components.
Developed responsive, user-centric frontend interfaces with React, implementing modern UI/UX patterns and ensuring cross-browser compatibility.
Established comprehensive CI/CD pipelines and automated testing suites using Jest and GitHub Actions, significantly reducing deployment errors and manual QA time.
Deployed and managed containerized applications on AWS cloud infrastructure using Docker and Kubernetes, leveraging serverless architectures (AWS Lambda) for cost-efficient scaling.
